---
title: Summery Pita Pizza Serves 1 | with Nectarine and Basil
description: This one-of-a-kind pizza combines the flavours of summer for a super speedy, satisfying lunch. Tear fragrant fresh basil over the top and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/summery-pita-pizza-bde6657b-fe4be065.jpg
